# Governance — nuxt-framework

> Generated from governance.md by crag. Regenerate: `crag compile --target cursor`

**Stack:** node, typescript, vue

## Quality Gates

Run these checks in order before committing:
### Lint
- `npm run lint`

### Test
- `npm run test`

### Build
- `npm run build`
- `npm run typecheck`

### Ci (inferred from workflow)
- `pnpm build`
- `pnpm lint:docs:fix`
- `pnpm test:engines:fix`
- `pnpm test:runtime -u`
- `pnpm test:unit -u`
- `pnpm lint:fix`
- `pnpm test:types`
- `pnpm lint`
## Security

- No hardcoded secrets — grep for sk_live, AKIA, password= before commit

## Conventions

- Conventional commits (feat:, fix:, docs:, etc.)
- Commit trailer: Co-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
- Runtimes: node
